section_a.beneficiaries: ..the people of Cuckfield and the surrounding area by hosting events with acclaimed authors and poets who discuss their work and the process of writing. The Cuckfield Bookfest aims to enrich the cultural life of the area by providing locals of all ages with the opportunity to engage with and be inspired by these authors and poets and through them, the process of writing and creativity. Where possible, opportunities will also be given to local authors to showcase their work. By including local people as volunteers, (catering, stewarding, hosting, etc), residents are involved in ensuring that the book festival remains a community event which people feel adds vigour to the life of the village
